### Get Analytics - Last 7 Days
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/analytics?period=7days
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Get Analytics - Last 90 Days
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/analytics?period=90days
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Get Analytics - Last 12 Months
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/analytics?period=12months
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Get Analytics - All Time
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/analytics?period=all
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

